Package com.fasterxml.clustermate.service.servlet

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    NodeMetricsServlet
    Stand-alone servlet that may be used for serving metrics information regarding this node (and possibly its peers as well)
    NodeStatusServlet
    Stand-alone servlet that may be used for serving node state information; usually not used, but can be used.
    RoutingEntryServlet<K extends EntryKey,E extends StoredEntry<K>>
    Specialized sub-type of Entry servlet that will either serve request locally (if data available), or return redirect code to indicate client who to call instead.
    ServiceDispatchServlet<K extends EntryKey,E extends StoredEntry<K>>
    "Uber-servlet" that is usually used to route requests to handlers (sync, node status, store), instead of handler-specific servlets.
    ServletBase  
    ServletServiceRequest
    ServiceRequest implemented over native Servlet request.
    ServletServiceResponse
    ServiceResponse implemented over native Servlet response.
    ServletWithMetricsBase
    Intermediate class we use to denote servlets that are to provide metrics information.
    StoreEntryServlet<K extends EntryKey,E extends StoredEntry<K>>
    Servlet that handles basic CRUD operations for individual entries.
    StoreListServlet<K extends EntryKey,E extends StoredEntry<K>>  
    SyncListServlet<K extends EntryKey,E extends StoredEntry<K>>  
    SyncPullServlet<K extends EntryKey,E extends StoredEntry<K>>
